$$\epsilon$$ (empty word) ($$A^0 = \{ epsilon \}$$)

$$A^*$$ is the set of finite words (Kleene's Star) ($$A^* = \bigcup_{n \in \mathscr{N}} A^n$$)

$$A^{n+1} = A^n . A = \{ wa | w \in A^n \land a \in A \}$$